title: David Wise - Star Fox Adventures (Gamerip 2002)
description:
Original upload credit goes to FFShrine Forums user fywfoe.

==================================================================================
Contains all of the tracks from the game, except for the ambient tracks; I'll
upload those later once I get the tags fixed. The album has 97 tracks and is in a
two-part zip. Part one has tracks 1-35 and part 2 has 36-97. Encoded at 192 cbr
mp3. This is the game rip that can be found on KH insider only things have been
fixed up a bit. (Copied from OP)
==================================================================================

I extracted both zip files and put them in one folder. The gamerip not only
contains original music, but unused music as well. It is well organized and a
hefty thanks to fywfoe for this unofficial release it so I could upload it as a
torrent for all to download, listen, and enjoy!
